sweep_points = [2]
nqubits = 3
k1 = ql.Kernel('kernel1', platf, nqubits)
k1.prepz(0)
k1.prepz(1)
k1.x(0)
k1.y(0)
k1.cnot(0, 1)
k1.toffoli(0, 1, 2)
k1.rx90(0)
k1.clifford(2, 0)
k1.measure(2)
k2 = ql.Kernel('kernel2', platf, nqubits)
k2.prepz(0)
k2.prepz(1)
k2.x(0)
k2.y(0)
k2.cnot(0, 1)
k2.toffoli(0, 1, 2)
k2.rx90(0)
k2.clifford(2, 0)
k2.measure(2)
p = ql.Program('aProgram', platf, nqubits)
p.set_sweep_points(sweep_points)
p.add_kernel(k1)
p.add_kernel(k2)
p.compile()
